3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper discusses Boolean Constraint Satisfaction Problems, which are relevant to the field of artificial intelligence and constraint programming. 
4. cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science): The paper deals with the complexity of satisfiability problems with different types of constraints, which is a topic of interest in mathematical logic and its applications in computer science. 
5. cs.DM (Discrete Mathematics): The paper involves the study of counting problems and their complexity, which is a topic of interest in discrete mathematics.
